data.description: Enjoy private country living close to town in this adorable 3-bedroom, 2-bath home in the heart of Fleming Island. Tucked away on a quiet, cul-de-sac street with no HOA & a huge 1/2 acre lot, this property lives larger than the square footage implies and offers everything you need in a home: open floor plan, large bedrooms, updated baths, 2-car garage, and a screened patio overlooking the private, fenced backyard complete with a heated/cooled workshop, storage shed, and a playhouse! Recent upgrades include interior paint, new tile flooring (no carpet!), new water heater (2024), updated primary bath with over-sized walk-in shower, updated fixtures, and oodles of charm! Seller will provide $7500 for kitchen upgrades with acceptable offer. All the major systems are either updated or in good working order, as well! Roof was replaced in 2012, HVAC in 2018, and septic was pumped and inspected in 2022. If you want a quiet, spacious move-in ready homes that is close to shopping and dining, look no further!
